        </div>

        <p class="text-[#edc92a] text-base font-medium mb-1 uppercase tracking-widest">Ramadhan Special</p>
        <h2 class="text-white text-[26px] lg:text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-2 drop-shadow-sm">
          Discount Up To <br/>
